works.additionalText:
Member of the Project Services team, responsible with the set-up and execution of research and activation studies. Member of a 
multi-disciplinary team that can manage projects from A to Z, from initial set-up document to preparing client-ready deliverables.

Key Responsibilities:
• Technical implementation of the online surveys using Decipher, Python, HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, in an efficient and 
effective way.
• Collaborate with the technical experts from the R&D team to take research forward for more complex and customized 
projects.
• Seek ways to optimize and automate processes where possible and suggest improvements to the clients about the project 
set-up.

Took on new responsibilities such as developing programming scripts to solve complex problems and mentoring and training new 
team members.
Key Responsibilities:
• Script online surveys using IBM SPSS Base Professional, update IIS layout with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript / jQuery, and use 
additional utilities for survey quality, such as DMQuery which used SQL syntax, and multi-language projects.
• Develop programming scripts to solve complex problems, mentor and train new team members, and work on challenging 
projects with complex modules.
• Coordinate with internal and external teams, offer alternative technical solutions to clients, and manage deadlines for various 
tasks.

Program online surveys using SPSS Data Collection, MySQL, HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, following customer guidelines and Ipsos 
standards.
Key Responsibilities:
• Script online surveys according to client materials using IBM SPSS Base Professional and update IIS layout using HTML, CSS, 
and JavaScript and collaborate with specialized teams for execution of advanced solutions and handling unexpected issues.
• Use additional utilities for survey quality and multi-language projects and test surveys for errors before resolving them on 
live projects.
• Coordinate with internal and external teams, offer alternative technical solutions to clients, and manage deadlines for various 
tasks.
